ich interpolates the\nAthanasopoulos-Caffarelli-Kenig-Salsa energy, thanks to the isoperimetric\ninequality.\n  In particular, we develop a detailed optimal regularity theory for the\nminimizers and for their free boundaries.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 1 Nov 2016 22:41:17 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 26 Jan 2017 18:39:30 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-01-27"}
