ty dynamics with a spin current and relaxation terms. We have\nshown that the motion of the conductance electron generates a magnetic torque\nand exerts a certain force on the helicoidal texture.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 2 Nov 2016 14:56:47 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-12-21"}
